Transform 'Scenario'. "crappy doc"

:-apply_transform(Signal, Transform, Output).

where T = transform(Type, Engine, SampleRate, StepSize, BlockSize, Parameters, Configuration, Program, WindowType, QueriedOutputsList)

where:

Type = effect;vamp

Engine = engine(API, PluginName, Version)

Sample Rate: if it is variable (mp4 stuff and streaming)

Step and Block Size when specifying framing

Parameters: VampParameter or LADSPA CONTROL PORTS

Configuration: extension for DSSI

Program: Vamp program

WindowType: Extension for frequency Signal

QueriedOutputs: Names of the outputs we desire to obtain in the transform (transform themselves)

Almost every parameters is optional: constraints and non deterministic calls...
